title: is there anyone who can dual a 1k stack nasus?
body:
I hate winning lane 5/0 then once he gets fh or visage, he just fks me, fks my jungler, fks my mid laner. 

 Is there anyone who can 1v1 a full late game nas? how do you build this mega champ? 

 I was playing gp and fking him , then 4 kills into him, he gets a frozen heart and pumps me in the butt.
